			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para><link xlink:href="https://www15.v1host.com/RACKSPCE/defect.mvc/Summary?oidToken=Defect%3A45242"
					>D-01588</link>: Scheduled Jobs - marker as query parameter does nothing</para>
